## Summary
This documentation outlines a six-step workflow for optimizing Amplitude to improve user engagement, covering the identification of critical events, determining product usage intervals, creating retention graphs, plotting user lifecycle graphs, mapping user personas, and comparing engagement across personas to maximize product value.

